{"tid":2137694,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴絲睇緊中環陳厚毅醫生?","createTime":"2020-08-03T06:18:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-05T20:04:54.000Z","uid":63750,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"975b39f77ebd8d2871d373790439191f4bd217f4","tid":2137694,"uid":63750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T06:18:09.000Z","msg":"我早排俾陳醫生昆左我around 4k part payment做個果酸treatment (full payment 係 8k)，俾左一半錢之後又叫我食A酸，食完個A酸又已經唔需要做果酸，個4k佢又唔肯退番俾我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以想問有無巴絲睇緊佢，睇下我可唔可以transfer 個 balance俾你用，唔想搞大佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有意留tg"},{"pid":"8ccdc3bd7754dd3e5ee6e4ae80e5076477e37584","tid":2137694,"uid":185376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T06:49:15.000Z","msg":"醫唔醫得好？"},{"pid":"ea1782d0b22ba66ffb45da98e0cc690f8b9a2a70","tid":2137694,"uid":63750,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8ccdc3bd7754dd3e5ee6e4ae80e5076477e37584","tid":2137694,"uid":185376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T06:49:15.000Z","msg":"醫唔醫得好？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T07:27:54.000Z","msg":"認真，好拖症，又收得貴<br />\n本身係出油問題，佢就開Ｄ抗生素俾我，食左幾個月，完全無好過，但就次次去覆診就話：好左好多喎！我好開心可以幫到你呀！<br />\n<br />\n之後我話無乜用，仲係好多油，仲搞到塊面紅卜卜，佢就叫我做果酸，做左5次，完全無分別，仲要次次做都等勁耐，之後話要做多5次先有效，我又俾佢昆到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最終果斷聽隔離A酸post巴打講，去左睇長陳，依家靚仔番哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"937f6acfe738f5e9fb7e463f3e4f252c57b5a584","tid":2137694,"uid":263774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T11:00:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eee196f04c873b99ee954b84f93e02f745c507d","tid":2137694,"uid":27664,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T11:04:17.0